casebody.data:
No. 9,

Orig.

United States v. Louisiana et al. (Louisiana Boundary Case) .

Report of Special Master received and ordered filed. Exceptions, if any, with supporting briefs to the Report may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Reply briefs, if any, to such exceptions may be filed within 30 days. Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this order. [For earlier orders herein, see, e. g., 409 U. S. 17 and 909.]
